  * Barnes & Noble '''Nook'''
  * iRiver Story & iRiver Cover Story : 현재 보유중인 기기
  * Sharp Zaurus, Nokia 770, n800, n810
  * Sony Reader
  * iPad, iPhone, iPod Touch (Lexcycle Stanza, Glider, iFlow Reader, iBooks)

